        Residential construction margins depend on the precision of the initial bid. Most builders rely on legacy spreadsheets that lack the dynamic data handling required for modern project management. This reliance on manual data entry introduces unnecessary risk. High-performing firms recognize that margin protection begins with a standardized, software-driven approach to quantity surveying and cost analysis.
      </p>
